## Common Patterns

### Pattern 1: Min/Max Functions

```aria
func:min = int64(int64:a, int64:b) {
    pass(is (a <=> b) < 0 : a : b);
};

func:max = int64(int64:a, int64:b) {
    pass(is (a <=> b) > 0 : a : b);
