### Pattern 3: Range Check

```aria
func:inRange = bool(int64:value, int64:min, int64:max) {
    pass((value <=> min) >= 0 && (value <=> max) <= 0);
};

bool:check = inRange(50, 0, 100);  // true
check = inRange(150, 0, 100);      // false
