### Pattern 4: Version Comparison

```aria
%STRUCT Version {
    int64:major,
    int64:minor,
    int64:patch
}

func:compareVersions = int64(Version:a, Version:b) {
    int64:majorCmp = a.major <=> b.major;
    if (majorCmp != 0) { pass(majorCmp); }

    int64:minorCmp = a.minor <=> b.minor;
