---

### Const vs Mutable

```aria
*const T   // const T* - read-only
*mut T     // T* - mutable
```

---

## Creating Pointers

### Address-of Operator

```aria
value: i32 = 42;
ptr: *i32 = &value;  // Get address of value
```

---

### From Array

```aria
arr: [i32; 10];
ptr: *i32 = &arr[0];  // Pointer to first element
```

---

### From C

```aria
extern "C" {
    fn malloc(size: usize) -> *void;
