## Methods

```aria
data: tensor<flt32, 3, 4> = create_tensor();

// Shape
shape: []i32 = data.shape();  // [3, 4]

// Reshape
reshaped: tensor<flt32, 4, 3> = data.reshape([4, 3]);

// Transpose
transposed: tensor<flt32, 4, 3> = data.transpose();

// Sum
total: flt32 = data.sum();

// Mean
average: flt32 = data.mean();
```

